movie_name: The Walking Dead: Daryl Dixon: The Return
short_description: Stars of The Walking Dead: Daryl Dixon (2023), Norman Reedus and Melissa McBride, revisit iconic moments between their characters, Daryl and Carol, and discuss what is coming up in season two of The Walking Dead: Daryl Dixon (2023).
